metadata.name: The Faces of Soul.
metadata.description:
We live hidden in a world more and more industrialized...more connected...more complex...we live waiting...This is the new world...and we have come so far.... 
new levels of emotional complexity...new ways of subsisting to weightless days, for not knowing how to live with ourselves, for not knowing when we lost our vital signs, for not knowing how to live without a mask....
